data.description: Welcome to Jerome Estates!  The pride of ownership shows throughout this home.  The additional upgrades are many: granite countertops, custom floor tile and LVP flooring in the bedrooms. The large living room has vaulted ceilings and is open to the dining room and kitchen.  The southwest facing backyard has a basket court, patio and large Storage shed.  An additional covered porch area is set back from the home and has a fire pit that is perfect for entertaining. Bring your RV and toys for plenty of room alongside the home. The inground sprinkler system keeps the rose garden and mature trees well maintained for easy upkeep. The spacious back yard is fully fenced. Please make an appointment to come see us soon!
